Package: optweight
Type: Package
Title: Covariate Balancing Weights Using Optimization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Noah Greifer [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Noah Greifer <noah.greifer@gmail.com>
Description: Use optimization to estimate weights that balance covariates for binary, multinomial, and longtiduinal treatments in the spirit of Zubizarreta (2015). The degree of balance can be specified for each covariate.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
    limSolve (>= 1.5.5.3)
Suggests:
    cobalt
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
